snippet.title: Rainbow Cotton - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Dreamcast revival of Rainbow Cotton is OUT NOW on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4/5, Xbox, and PC (Steam)! 👉 https://www.iningames.com/games/rainbow-cotton

#RainbowCotton is an easy-to-learn, pick-up-and-play rail shooter or, in the manner of the Series, rail cuter if you want! Accompany Cotton and the little Silk on one of their iconic, whacky adventures! Can you get Cotton her beloved and well deserved Willows?

🔹 Nintendo Switch 👉 https://www.nintendo.com/en-gb/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/Rainbow-Cotton-2551327.html
🔹 Xbox 👉 https://www.xbox.com/en-GB/games/store/rainbow-cotton/9NR9DDHZJ2F7/0017
🔹 PS 👉 https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10009332
🔹 Steam 👉https://store.steampowered.com/app/2729600/Rainbow_Cotton/

#cotton #dreamcast #RainbowCotton #anime #memes #gaming
